                        <additions>
                            <list> 
                                <item xml:id="a1">
                                <locus target="#188v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">A short section on the Law,  in a modern hand. </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ኦሪት፡ ብሃል፡ ዜና። እስመ፡ ይትናገር፡ ዜና፡ አበዉ።  
                                        ደግመኒ፡ ብሄለ፡ ሕግ፡ ወስምዕ፡ እስመ፡ ሀለው፡ ቦቱ፡ ሕግ፡ ወስምዕ። ዓዲ፡ ደሰመይ፡ ብርሃነ፡ በልሳነ፡ ሶርያ። ወሀለው፡ ዉስቴቱ፡ ፱ነገሬት፡ ዘዉእቶሙ፡ ጥበብ፡ ሥጋዊ፡</q>
                                    <note>Then follow other short sections, on the comparison of the Law, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ምስሌሁ፡ ለኦሪት፡</foreign> ; on the four causes of the creation of the world, 
                                        <foreign xml:lang="gez">ምክንያታተ፡ ፍጥረተ፡ ዓለም፡ ፬እሙንቱ፡</foreign>;   and on the nature of air and fire, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ባሕርዩ፡ ለነፉስ፡ ዉዕየት፡ ወርጥበት። ወባሕርዩ፡ ለእሳት፡ ዉዕ የት፡ ወይብሰት፡</foreign> etc.</note>
                            </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <locus target="#1r #18r #26r"/>
                                    <desc type="Unclear">The names at the foot of ff. 1r, 18r and 26r are probably those of the three scribes, <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11358WaldaG">Walda Giyorgis</persName>, 
                                        <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11359Giyorgis">Giyorgis</persName>, and <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11360Adara">ʾAdarā Krǝstos</persName>.</desc>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a3">
                                    <locus target="#2r"/>
                                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">The note states that the manuscript belongs to the church of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0101MadhaneAlam">Madḫāne ʿAlam</placeName>
                                    </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ሄኖክ፡ ዘመ'፡ ዓለም።</q>
                                </item>
                                
                            </list>
                        </additions>
                        
